      "text": [
        "590 - وَقَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ فِي آخِرِ حَدِيثٍ طَوِيلٍ: «يَصِفُ فِيهِ غُسْلَ اَلْمَيِّتِ لاَ تُخَلِّلْ أَظَافِيرَهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.590 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said at the end of a long narration describing the washing of the deceased:\n\"Do not interlace (clean) the fingernails”."
        ]
      }
    }
  },
